00:38.536 --> 00:40.540
‐ [whines]

00:40.540 --> 00:42.836
<i>[typewriter keys clack]</i>

00:42.836 --> 00:44.548
JOY: [voice echoing]
Mom?

00:44.548 --> 00:46.760
‐ [panting]
JOY: Mom?

00:46.760 --> 00:49.600
Mom, what are you looking at?

00:49.600 --> 00:51.352
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:51.352 --> 00:53.398
Did something happen?

00:53.398 --> 00:56.655
ANNIE: [panting]

00:56.655 --> 00:58.784
‐ Mom!

00:58.784 --> 01:01.790
<i>[intense music]</i>

01:01.790 --> 01:04.921
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:04.921 --> 01:08.804
<i>[music fades]</i>

01:08.804 --> 01:11.810
<i>[dog growling, barking]</i>

01:11.810 --> 01:15.108
